OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778351315
OL,3,CMan who fed four-year-old girl heroin
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FA man who was jailed after feeding
OL,7,Fdrugs to his partner's four-year-old
OL,8,Fdaughter has died in prison.
OL,10,FJohn Rytting died at HMP Hull, where
OL,11,Fhe was serving a 13-year sentence, on
OL,12,F22 April, the Prisons and Probation
OL,13,FOmbudsman said.
OL,15,FA spokesperson said an independent
OL,16,Finvestigation would now take place.
OL,18,F"We will make our final investigation
OL,19,Freport public after the inquest
OL,20,Fconcludes," they said.
