OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778351315
OL,3,CMan who fed four-year-old girl heroin
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FRytting and his parter, Michala Pyke,
OL,7,Fwere jailed in 2017 for child cruelty
OL,8,Fand supplying drugs.
OL,10,FThe couple fed Pyke's four-year-old
OL,11,Fdaughter Poppy Widdison a combination
OL,12,Fof drugs including heroin and ketamine.
OL,14,FAt the time, the court heard they saw
OL,15,FPoppy as an "inconvenience" to their
OL,16,Frelationship.
OL,18,FPoppy died in June 2013 after
OL,19,Fsuffering a cardiac arrest in
OL,20,FRytting's "squalid" home in Grimsby.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
