FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778351315
OL,3,CMan who fed four-year-old girl heroin
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination found she
OL,7,Fhad ingested a variety of drugs for up
OL,8,Fto six months before her death, but
OL,9,Fthat they did not contribute to her
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FHowever, jurors heard there was a
OL,13,F"long period of ill-treatment and
OL,14,Fneglect by the grossly inappropriate
OL,15,Fadministration of various drugs"
OL,16,Fbefore her death.
OL,18,FThe judge told Pyke: "You drugged that
OL,19,Fchild for your own squalid reasons."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
