OL,3,CMan who fed four-year-old girl heroin
OL,4,Cdies in prison
OL,6,FPyke was described as "utterly unfit"
OL,7,Fto be a mother and a liar whose
OL,8,Fexpressions of love towards Poppy
OL,9,Fduring the trial were "a despicable
OL,10,Fmasquerade".
